---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <nav>
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="logo">Carevues</a>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about" class="active">About</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <article>
    <div class="container article-body">
      <header class="article-header">
        <span class="category">About</span>
        <h1>About Carevues</h1>
        <p class="description">Helping Australians make smarter health and wellness decisions.</p>
      </header>

      <div class="article-content">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>Carevues is an Australian health and wellness review site focused on two of the most important areas of modern life: <strong>mental health</strong> and <strong>sleep quality</strong>.</p>

        <p>We research, test, and review the apps, platforms, and products that claim to help — and we tell you honestly what works, what doesn't, and what's worth your money.</p>

        <h2>What We Review</h2>
        <p>Our review categories include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Online therapy platforms</strong> — BetterHelp, Talkspace, and other telehealth mental health services available in Australia</li>
          <li><strong>Sleep technology</strong> — sleep trackers, smart mattresses, wearables</li>
          <li><strong>Health and wellness apps</strong> — meditation, nutrition, fitness</li>
          <li><strong>Supplements and products</strong> — with honest assessments of the evidence</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Review Process</h2>
        <p>Every review on Carevues is based on:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Direct experience with the platform or product where possible</li>
          <li>Analysis of user reviews from Australians (Trustpilot, ProductReview.com.au, Google)</li>
          <li>Comparison against current Australian market alternatives</li>
          <li>Transparent pricing in AUD, updated regularly</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
        <p>Carevues.com.au uses affiliate links. This means we may earn a commission when you click a link to a product or service and make a purchase — <strong>at no extra cost to you</strong>.</p>

        <p>The commission helps us keep the site running and continue publishing free, honest reviews. We only link to products and services we genuinely recommend. Our editorial content is not influenced by affiliate partnerships.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Have a suggestion for a product or service you'd like us to review? Get in touch at <strong>hello@carevues.com.au</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>Carevues.com.au — Honest health and wellness reviews for Australians.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
